: 0.1109, "y": 0.125, "width": 0.7788, "height": 0.1799}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.125}, {"x": 0.8897, "y": 0.125}, {"x": 0.8897, "y": 0.3049}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.3049}], "comment": "The discussion of environmental values hindering knowledge generation adds a valuable perspective on how conflicting values impact research trajectories.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "25c77dce-3838-4dd5-b2c4-456e43244354", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.688, "width": 0.758, "height": 0.18370000000000009}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.688}, {"x": 0.8695, "y": 0.688}, {"x": 0.8695, "y": 0.8717}, {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.8717}], "comment": "The sentence truncation (\u00e2\u0080\u009cthe women\u00e2\u0080\u0099s limited\u00e2\u0080\u009d) disrupts clarity; the student should complete this thought to maintain coherence in the argument.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "f14c7880-e9ce-4d71-9135-e8e50b9806dc", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 5, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.1207, "width": 0.7745, "height": 0.2231}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.1207}, {"x": 0.8854, "y": 0.1207}, {"x": 0.8854, "y": 0.3438}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.3438}], "comment": "\u00e2\u0080\u009cSuppression of knowledge\u00e2\u0080\u009d is mentioned without unpacking which values led to marginalization of contributors; the analysis needs specific examples linking values to exclusion.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "e9f8db2a-7816-41a4-872c-203ed298d43a", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "general", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.1305, "y": 0.125, "width": 0.7469999999999999, "height": 0.0857}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1305, "y": 0.125}, {"x": 0.8775, "y": 0.125}, {"x": 0.8775, "y": 0.2107}, {"x": 0.1305, "y": 0.2107}], "comment": "Important TOK concepts (e.g., communities of knowers, suppression of knowledge) appear but often lack analytical unpacking; deeper conceptual engagement is needed throughout.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "af60e1e1-4345-4c01-b028-05626a4f3b24", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 5, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.4029, "width": 0.7868, "height": 0.2657}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.4029}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.4029}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.6686}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.6686}], "comment": "The claim that national power motivated knowledge production would be strengthened by linking to historical policies or funding patterns, rather than a general assertion.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "7104079e-7904-4ea0-8d9e-89de19002da3", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 5, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.7268, "width": 0.7868, "height": 0.1018}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.7268}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.7268}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.8286}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.8286}], "comment": "The concluding sentence effectively ties the analysis back to the core theme, emphasizing how values shape both the creation and interpretation of knowledge.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "d5ce4954-5024-44c3-8905-8c768c12228b", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 6, "bbox": {"x": 0.3205, "y": 0.2429, "width": 0.3529, "height": 0.020799999999999985}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.3205, "y": 0.2429}, {"x": 0.6734, "y": 0.2429}, {"x": 0.6734, "y": 0.2637}, {"x": 0.3205, "y": 0.2637}], "comment": "\u00e2\u0080\u009cExhibit 3: Atanasoff-Berry Computer\u00e2\u0080\u009d is clearly labeled, maintaining consistency in exhibit presentation.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "628de50f-d9e5-43e5-b2ae-6c3531e47cd4", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "general", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.643, "width": 0.7776, "height": 0.22250000000000003}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.643}, {"x": 0.8885, "y": 0.643}, {"x": 0.8885, "y": 0.8655}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.8655}], "comment": "The reference to Popper\u00e2\u0080\u0099s provisionality is interesting but remains unconnected to the central question of how values shape knowledge production; deeper analytical linkage is needed.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "17b93968-5f24-4c8d-962b-790f3815f41d", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 6, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.2969, "width": 0.7776, "height": 0.3049}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.2969}, {"x": 0.8885, "y": 0.2969}, {"x": 0.8885, "y": 0.6018}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.6018}], "comment": "The use of precise funding figures ($206.9 million, $97.8 billion) provides strong empirical support for the argument about economic values influencing research.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "b5a4aa0b-95ac-409a-9ef0-c2dbf61dfb6a", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 6, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.6359, "width": 0.7745, "height": 0.2249}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.6359}, {"x": 0.8854, "y": 0.6359}, {"x": 0.8854, "y": 0.8608}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.8608}], "comment": "The assertion that \u00e2\u0080\u009cpower as a nation is the ultimate goal\u00e2\u0080\u009d is overgeneralized; the student should unpack how innovation values translated into concrete policy or institutional decisions.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "aa1166cb-bda7-4cb6-a9f1-13ae1292ca55", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 7, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.1207, "width": 0.7359, "height": 0.063}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.1207}, {"x": 0.8468, "y": 0.1207}, {"x": 0.8468, "y": 0.1837}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.1837}], "comment": "The causal link between military power and knowledge production is asserted but needs clearer explanation of mechanisms (for example, defense funding or strategic research initiatives).", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "1c69d114-0907-43f8-9957-a63cb7d69f52", "versionId": "c7d2c6bc-a827-440e-a4f3-3a37ea4853d2", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 7, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.2178, "width": 0.777, "height": 0.18280000000000002}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.2178}, {"x": 0.8879, "y": 0.2178}, {"x": 0.8879, "y": 0.4006}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.4006}], "comment": "The analysis of cultural values remains broad; specify which cultural norms influenced research priorities and illustrate their impact on knowledge production.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}]}]}}, "rubricData": {"id": 57, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "version": 1, "status": "published", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:43.512632+00", "totalMarks": 10, "description": null, "type": "TOK", "rubricSpecificInfo": null, "tags": [""], "isArchived": false, "gradeBoundaryId": "52ad2701-27bc-42f3-be3f-d63b98d98139", "name": "TOK Exhibition", "slug": "tok-exhibition", "rubricCriteria": [{"id": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "revisionId": 57, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition", "label": null, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:55.358727+00", "updatedAt": "2025-07-16 11:21:18.828885+00", "isGradable": true, "showGradedScore": true, "isChecklistCriterion": false, "description": null, "rubricCriterionBands": [{"id": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 0, "marksTo": 0, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:46.486581+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f7cb0652-0737-403e-8f65-be13bd2fd7f1", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "content": "The exhibition does not reach the standard described by the other levels or does not use one of the IA prompts provided.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:58.577216+00"}]}, {"id": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 1, "marksTo": 2, "orderIndex": 1, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:47.076074+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "861f06ce-2b51-46ce-a6ee-3022e7080288", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "content": "The exhibition presents\nthree objects, but the\nreal-world contexts of\nthese objects are not\nstated, or the images\npresented may be\nhighly generic images of\ntypes of object rather\nthan of specific\nreal-world objects. Links\nbetween the objects\nand the selected IA\nprompt are made, but\nthese are minimal,\ntenuous, or it is not\nclear what the student is\ntrying to convey.\nThere is very little\njustification offered for\nthe inclusion of each\nobject in the exhibition.\nThe commentary on the\nobjects is highly\ndescriptive or consists\nonly of unsupported\nassertions.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:04.443183+00"}]}, {"id": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 3, "marksTo": 4, "orderIndex": 2, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.072006+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "e8acd337-a77d-4319-a744-06094151d57b", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of the objects may be implied rather than explicitly stated. Basic links between the objects and the selected IA prompt are made, but the explanation of these links is unconvincing and/or unfocused. There is a superficial justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Reasons for the inclusion of the objects are offered, but these are not supported by appropriate evidence and/or lack relevance to the selected IA prompt. There may be significant repetition across the justifications of the different objects", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:20.428881+00"}]}, {"id": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 5, "marksTo": 6, "orderIndex": 3, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.868343+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "c257e18a-e3b8-46f4-b3b9-d9ea5cd5db84", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of these objects may be vaguely or imprecisely stated. There is some explanation of the links between the three objects and the selected IA prompt. There is some justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Some of the points are supported by evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:31.312862+00"}]}, {"id": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 7, "marksTo": 8, "orderIndex": 4, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:49.555746+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f16fe76e-abd8-4dc1-9a4f-50ab9e121c99", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects and their real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are explained, although this explanation may lack precision and clarity in parts. There is a justification of the contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. Many of the points are supported by appropriate evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:40.123527+00"}]}, {"id": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 9, "marksTo": 10, "orderIndex": 5, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:50.346899+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "055fe2ad-3ef1-4074-af44-83cc3440cc7a", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "content": "The exhibition clearly identifies three objects and their specific real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are clearly made and well-explained. There is a strong justification of the particular contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. All, or nearly all, of the points are well-supported by appropriate evidence and explicit references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:51.46084+00"}]}], "rubricCriterionStrands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:59.452498+00", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?"}]}]}, "similarExemplars": [{"id": "8a3d9685-2b22-4de1-a016-66aa42c73f15", "title": "In What Ways Do Our Values Affect Our Acquisition of Knowledge?", "description": "", "tags": ["grade-B", "tok", "sl"], "slug": "in-what-ways-do-our-values-affect-our-acquisition-of", "isPublic": true, "isPremium": true, "showScores": true, "createdAt": "2025-08-05T07:46:21.656Z", "userSubmissionId": "da43f4f9-78d3-4419-a3be-b8474bcd1eaa", "submissionId": "4f250aea-7cfb-4962-a621-7bd12b2697cc", "similarity": 0.532028154, "normalizedScore": 0.8, "compositeScore": 0.6124197078, "matchingFileId": "", "matchingChunkId": "", "matchingChunkNumber": 0, "userSubmission": {"id": "da43f4f9-78d3-4419-a3be-b8474bcd1eaa", "score": "B", "scoreType": "letter", "level": null, "researchQuestion": null, "tokPrompt": null, "title": " In What Ways Do Our Values Affect Our Acquisition of Knowledge?", "cohort": null, "createdAt": "2025-07-14T18:34:11.015Z", "subjectId": 582, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "subject": {"id": 582, "title": "Theory of Knowledge (TOK)",